    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle offering an affordable entry point for daily transportation or a practical project. This car shows its age and wear, but it still presents a solid opportunity for the right buyer who values price, utility, and potential. Priced to sell and represented with transparency, it\u2019s a sensible option for shoppers looking for dependable value without a big upfront cost.",
