    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runaround or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t winning any beauty contests, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone handy or anyone needing basic transport without spending a fortune. A great chance to pick up a car at an accessible price and make it your own.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with real enthusiast potential. This car is in poor cosmetic and overall condition, but it still offers a fundamentally capable platform with a willing powertrain, complete chassis, and plenty of usable hard parts. Engine bay presents as largely intact, the driveline feels like a worthwhile starting point, and it\u2019s a great candidate for a budget build, track toy, or parts-forward restoration. If you know how to turn wrenches, there\u2019s value here in the mechanical package alone. Priced to move for someone who sees the upside.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest transportation. Rough around the edges, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A scrappy, honest ride with plenty of story left to tell, this car is perfect for someone who sees opportunity where others see age. It has the kind of seasoned character that makes every errand feel a little more adventurous, and it could be a great fit for a handy owner, a project-minded driver, or anyone needing simple, affordable wheels. If you want something inexpensive with personality and potential, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project opportunity. It shows age and wear consistent with a well-used car, but it still presents a cost-effective path into ownership at an accessible price point. A smart buy for shoppers who prioritize affordability and utility.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a good starter project. It shows its age and has some wear, which is reflected in the price, but it still has real value for the right buyer. I like to be upfront, and if you\u2019re after an honest car at a reasonable price, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project candidate with strong enthusiast appeal. This car presents in rough cosmetic shape, but it still offers a usable drivetrain, responsive steering feel, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it an excellent budget entry point for a hands-on owner. Starts, runs, and delivers the raw, analog character many newer cars lack. Ideal for someone looking for an affordable driver, weekend tinkering platform, or restoration base. Priced to move for its condition while leaving room for improvements.",
